## Flujo de Datos

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant T as TUI
    participant F as fff.odin
    participant C as libfff_c
    participant R as Rust Core
    
    U->>T: Open FFF Search View
    T->>F: fff_create(base_path)
    F->>C: fff_create_instance()
    C->>R: Create FilePicker
    R-->>C: Return handle
    C-->>F: Return FffResult
    F-->>T: Return FileFinder
    
    T->>F: fff_start_scan()
    F->>C: fff_scan_files()
    C->>R: Background scan
    
    loop User types query
        U->>T: Type character
        T->>F: fff_fuzzy_search(query)
        F->>C: fff_search(handle, query)
        C->>R: Fuzzy match
        R-->>C: JSON results
        C-->>F: FffResult with data
        F->>F: json.unmarshal()
        F-->>T: FffSearchResult
        T->>U: Render results
    end
    
    U->>T: Select item
    T->>F: fff_track_selection()
    F->>C: fff_track_query()
    C->>R: Update frecency
```

